{"tid":1499660,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"其實,到今時今日仲覺得報警有用嘅人係太天真定係乜","createTime":"2019-08-23T19:49:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-28T13:37:35.000Z","uid":6571,"like":58,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4413b36c5bed653eef7125d50ec321ec10badd53","tid":1499660,"uid":6571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:49:03.000Z","msg":"都做晒出面選擇性執法<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n你比人打完報警唔係信打你嗰位會有事下話<br />\n你話成抽記者影住就話唔還拖姐<br />\n<br />\n善良冇問題<br />\n但係你嘅善良係咁比人利用嘅時候係唔係需要放低佢呢<br />\n<br />\n中學係咁比人恰嘅毒撚都有爆seed嘅時候啦<br />\n係唔係到比人傷害到不可逆轉嘅情況之下先醒起可以還拖呢?"},{"pid":"7c2c297b13d1e6edd9d4c794db1348e98a04f3c8","tid":1499660,"uid":37504,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:51:22.000Z","msg":"報警肯定無用啦<br />\n<br />\n比人打唔該要還手<br />\n<br />\n兩個幾月啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"541287fa2acfb21b2c2484bef58a13930c568c13","tid":1499660,"uid":119467,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:51:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"00e2d1cfeaf9f2502a9bd82fc4e7af1446d0ab86","tid":1499660,"uid":75823,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:52:39.000Z","msg":"比人插到爆江入院你報警還可<br />\n一般打鬥？"},{"pid":"3687423ccf0028c2970ac4dfe31d7d0734072abe","tid":1499660,"uid":135276,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:53:07.000Z","msg":"思想太戇鳩，仲未醒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0de4bafc6b177eae95eae729f64ceec2f77c9144","tid":1499660,"uid":286964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T19:53:32.000Z","msg":"借位<br />\n<br />\n被控義士們依家點？<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1499004\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1499004</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"222dec522c9a54df5dace50f027923c556861c6c","tid":1499660,"uid":8948,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"00e2d1cfeaf9f2502a9bd82fc4e7af1446d0a